{
  "stem": "13096.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But what we didn't like, it was-- it was a row-- a row-- a big table-- a row of German officers sitting with chairs there-- about 10 to 12 officers.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the middle of all these people was Mengele, that doctor they used to call the Angel of Death.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from far away, dressed as we were, and everything-- dressed as we were to-- with everything, he start, you know, selecting people-- which one to go to the right, which one to go to the left.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't know what it means to the right, to the left, to the right, to the left.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Eventually, we knew the people who went to the right was to go to the concentrations camp, to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Birkenau, it was the camp that we arrive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The one to the left were send-- they were waiting for them some lorries.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they took them away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we say goodbye.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we ask the prisoner that they were in charge, you know, translating the-- what it was-- you know, what it was happening.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they say, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They are old people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They are tired.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They are going to be transported, you know, to their places, you know, where they are going to rest.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They didn't want to upset us, because they were prisoner like us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And amongst them, there were people who was speak Spanish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were from Salonika, and they were all taken before us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Actually, in Salonika, which was in Greece, there were, before the war, 40,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they came back about-- not even 100.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
